                <li>Direct publishing to WordPress, Ghost, Webflow, Shopify</li>
                <li>Bundle adds local SEO + rank tracking at $167/mo</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>No per-article purchase — monthly subscription only</li>
                <li>Focused on long-form blog, not landing pages</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Owner-operators who want articles published, not just drafted.</div>
