          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Solo bloggers and small WordPress businesses on tight budget.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/koala-ai/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read Koala review →</a>
